<exploration xml:id="warm-cuantosVes-dedosEnDosManos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Warm-up: Cuántos ves: Dedos en dos manos (10 minutes)</title>

<statement>
  <p>¿Cómo sabes cuántos dedos ves?</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses: </p>
<ul>
      <li>5: I know we have 5 fingers on each hand.</li>
      <li>6: I counted 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, and 6.</li>
      <li>7: I know one hand is 5 and then 6 and 7.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


